          "original": "The gas-atomized Al5Ti5 HEA powders with an average particle size of 36.36 μm were used to fabricate Al5Ti5 bulk specimens. The SLM was performed using a laser powder-bed-fusion (LPBF) printer (SLM-100, Guangdong Hanbang) under an argon atmosphere with optimized printing parameters (laser power: 175 W, scan speed: 1000 mm/s, layer thickness: 30 μm, hatching space: 80 μm).",
